<h1>2016 SVP Chicago Letter of Interest </h1>
<h2>Sector Focus:  Breaking the Cycle of Poverty</h2>
<h3>Completing this Form:</h3>
<p>Please enter information directly into the form, using this form as the main body of your Letter of Interest.</p>
<ul>
  <li>If you find an item confusing, please feel free to contact us.</li>
  <li>Please use bullet points rather than paragraphs.</li>
  <li>Brevity is helpful to our partners when reviewing proposals.</li>
</ul>
<form class="form-horizontal" role="form" method="post" action="/letter_of_interest">

<!-- section 1 -->
<%= render partial: "partials/contact_info" %>

<!-- section 2 -->
